title: [Ta'Illistim, Caear Var]
description: The cobblestoned var intersects from three directions, the polished granite stones gleaming in their varied hues of grey, blue and dusky rose.  Traffic flows around a small statue that stands at the center of the convergence.

The cobblestoned var intersects from three directions, the polished granite stones gleaming in their varied hues of grey, blue and silver.  Traffic flows around a small statue that stands at the center of the convergence.
